data.description: A well maintained, beautiful brick ranch home located on an exclusive corner lot.  Come enjoy one level living with easy-care vinyl flooring throughout and ceramic tile in the bathrooms and kitchen, plus stainless steel appliances . This home offer endless entertaining possibilities with built in surround sound speakers in the living room and a partially fenced in back yard with a deck.  This home has a new roof and a new water heater. Conveniently located near parks, museums, shopping, entertainment, and more!
